    "description": "Skate through the icy and labyrinthine depths of Icemaze Cave. Can you find your way out?<br><br><strong>Icemaze Cave: Skate Escape</strong> is a 2D logic puzzle game about path planning with exploration and collection elements, inspired by familiar retro adventure games.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1834120/extras/cab00a550d1e5c35c5a58ccb33ad6821.poster.avif?t=1726412886\" width=320 height=180 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1834120/extras/cab00a550d1e5c35c5a58ccb33ad6821.webm?t=1726412886\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1834120/extras/cab00a550d1e5c35c5a58ccb33ad6821.mp4?t=1726412886\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Explore the increasingly complex cave rooms. Find your way across the icy floors to the exit. Along the way, you may find valuable minerals worthy of a detour. Or perhaps you'd rather avoid detours altogether, using your expert navigational skills to stay on the shortest path out.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Features</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> Explore 100 levels of increasing difficulty, each with a different cave layout and a puzzle for you to solve.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1834120/extras/828b8700a9b5e65b97a13645c3b322d6.poster.avif?t=1726412886\" width=320 height=180 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1834120/extras/828b8700a9b5e65b97a13645c3b322d6.webm?t=1726412886\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1834120/extras/828b8700a9b5e65b97a13645c3b322d6.mp4?t=1726412886\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br></li><li> Collect valuable minerals along the way by solving the 100 complementary puzzles.<br></li><li> Push your navigational skills to the limit to find the most efficient solutions for additional rewards.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1834120/extras/a4bbd3621fcd3b91be7d66766a67122a.poster.avif?t=1726412886\" width=320 height=180 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1834120/extras/a4bbd3621fcd3b91be7d66766a67122a.webm?t=1726412886\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1834120/extras/a4bbd3621fcd3b91be7d66766a67122a.mp4?t=1726412886\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br></li><li> Stimulate your mental acuity by exercising spatial memorization and path planning.<br></li><li> Enjoy the nostalgic style reminiscent of familiar retro adventure games.</li></ul>",
